  <brief_title>The Effect of EGD Scope Insertion on the Intracuff Pressure of a New, Modified LMA in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Esophagogastroduodenoscopy Scope Insertion on the Intracuff Pressure of a New, Modified Laryngeal Mask Airway in Children</official_title>
