  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this current study is to compare changes of the intracuff pressure in the
      newly designed LMA with the older design LMA after insertion of an esophagogastroduodenoscopy
      (EGD) probe in pediatric patients and adolescents.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
